About Us

Who are we?

We are a leading Early Childhood Education company in India with over 15 years of experience, dedicated to Harnessing the Genius of Early Childhood. Our mission is to support parents and preschool educators in fostering the all-round growth and success of children through our innovative Hands-on…Minds-on learning approach. Proud winners of numerous awards, we excel in creating and utilizing the best preschool curriculum, preschool books, education technology, teacher training, activity kits, Montessori materials, and the best preschool materials. Our resources are designed to benefit students, parents, and our partner preschool franchises in achieving excellence in early childhood learning. Recognized as the best preschool franchise in India, we provide extensive support to ensure the success of each franchise. Our talented team, led by IIT-IIM alumni, is passionate about delivering exceptional learning and developmental outcomes for children.

End-to-End Setup and Launch Strategy

We guide you through every step, from choosing the best location and designing engaging learning spaces to obtaining necessary approvals and ensuring child safety. Our support includes customized preschool marketing strategies, social media promotion, and grand opening events to maximize visibility and impact. With our expertise, your preschool franchise will excel in attracting parents searching for a "preschool near me," ensuring success in the competitive landscape of early childhood education in India.


Vast In-House Expertise and Capabilities

We deliver a comprehensive preschool ecosystem, providing preschool operational support, Ed-tech solutions with preschool books, preschool apps, and learning portals. Partner with us to create a leading preschool franchise that excels in early childhood education in India.

14. Bright Concept Teacher

15. Overview of Do-It-Yourself: Multi-Intelligence

DIY:MI is an innovative approach for preschool franchises that engages children in a "Hands-on, Minds-on" program, keeping them away from mobile screens. This method helps active parental involvement in their child's development and enhances the preschool curriculum with engaging activities.

16. Bright Beep

Bright Beep is a comprehensive school app that facilitates two-way communication with parents. Beyond messaging, it offers a range of features including sharing notices, photos, managing the Toy Library, and managing school fees.
